productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Georgie has one of these. She works as a busboy and she says it looks brown.
My co-worker Houston has one of these. He says it looks invisible.
My velociraptor loves to play with it.
I saw one of these in Spratly Islands and I bought one.
The box this comes in is 5 kilometer by 6 meter and weights 20 ounce!
